features: [TWO WAYS OF CHARGING]With both a QI charging panel and USB charging port, this bright desk lamp gives you the option to use wireless or wired charging. In addition, the USB port can also be used to power a small fan, providing a cool breeze during summer.

[KEEP DESK ALWAYS ORGANIZED] This desk lamp for home office comes with a storage space for small items like pens, pencils, and glasses. It helps keep your workspace clean and organized, saving you space and creating a clutter-free environment.

[ADJUSTABLE COLOR TEMPERATURE AND BRIGHTNESS]With 3 lighting modes and brightness levels, this dimmable table lamp with wireless charger allows you to adjust the light to meet your different needs when reading, studying or working.

[EYE-CARING DESK LAMP]The soft, stable, and non-flickering light of this study desk lamp helps reduce eye fatigue and avoid radiation. With a high CRI of 90+, it provides an accurate color portrayal, creating a comfortable and healthy lighting environment.

[ADJUSTABLE ARM FOR PERFECT LIGHT ANGLE] This table lamp with pen holder features a flexible arm that can be easily adjusted to any angle and height. Whether you're working, reading, or just relaxing, you can adjust the lamp to your desired angle for optimal lighting.

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on February 8, 2024
reviews.reviewTitle: 5.0 out of 5 stars “I must say, it has exceeded my expectations.”
reviews.reviewText: I recently purchased this desk lamp with a wireless charger, pencil holder, and adjustable features, and I must say, it has exceeded my expectations. The sleek design fits perfectly on my desk without taking up too much space, and the addition of a wireless charger is incredibly convenient for keeping my devices powered up throughout the day.The adjustable lamp feature allows me to customize the lighting to suit my needs, whether I'm working late into the night or reading a book in the evening. The brightness levels are just right, providing ample light without being harsh on the eyes.

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on November 1, 2023
reviews.reviewTitle: 5.0 out of 5 stars Wireless iphone charger
reviews.reviewText: I recently purchased a dimmable lamp with a wireless charger, and I must say it has quickly become an indispensable addition to my workspace. Here are some key highlights from my experience:Versatility: This lamp serves multiple purposes. The dimmable LED lighting is perfect for adjusting the brightness to suit different tasks, whether it's reading, working on my computer, or setting a cozy mood in the room. The wireless charger is a game-changer, allowing me to charge my phone or other Qi-compatible devices conveniently.Sleek and modern design: The lamp's design is not only functional but also aesthetically pleasing. Its modern and minimalist look fits well with various interior styles, and it doesn't take up much space on my desk.Convenient charging: The wireless charger works flawlessly. I just place my phone on the charging pad, and it starts charging immediately. There's no need to fumble with cords, making it incredibly convenient, especially when I need to charge my phone quickly during work.I highly recommend it to anyone looking to enhance their workspace or add a touch of modernity to their home.

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on January 14, 2024
reviews.reviewTitle: 5.0 out of 5 stars Great nighttime reading light
reviews.reviewText: This is a perfect small lamp for bedtime reading. Husband says the light is easier on his eyes than his old lamp and he likes the holder cup for his reading glasses. The only negative is the wireless charging function doesn't work as well as expected. In the upright position the phone easily slips off if bumped in the slightest. iPhone mini 13 charged pretty slowly and the charger got pretty warm. Not sure if it was the phone case that made the wireless charging difficult but we switched to using the USB port and that worked fine.

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on July 18, 2023
reviews.reviewTitle: 4.0 out of 5 stars Adjustable light intensity
reviews.reviewText: The lamp is a great addition to my study table. The adjustable lights and wireless- charger is very useful. I also loved how the light intensities and the warm/cool lights are adjustable to the different levels. Definitely, recommend one.

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on January 31, 2024
reviews.reviewTitle: 5.0 out of 5 stars Love how it had a wireless charging option for my phone!
reviews.reviewText: The combination of wireless charger and pen holder is so cool! Bonus that it comes with a light. Easy to install and use as well.

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on February 12, 2024
reviews.reviewTitle: 5.0 out of 5 stars All in One Solution
reviews.reviewText: This fits perfectly on my night stand- I like to keep my phone handy at night- and this fits and charges my 12 Pro perfectly. Also love the pen holder and different color modes on the light! Super functional and nice modern look.

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on February 9, 2024
reviews.reviewText: I purchased this desk lamp mainly to point the light at myself during video conferencing, as my current lighting setup is too dark. The light is surprisingly brighter than I expected, which is very convenient for my use case. The light can also be dimmed if needed. The ability to charge my phone and store pens is a bonus for me.
